OL,3,CTwo men charged in investigation into
OL,4,Ccross-border terrorism
OL,6,FTwo men are to appear in court in Co
OL,7,FLaois charged in connection with an
OL,8,Finvestigation into cross-border
OL,9,Fterrorism.
OL,11,FThe men, both in their 30s, were
OL,12,Farrested in Limerick and Portlaoise on
OL,13,FThursday and will appear before
OL,14,FPortlaoise District Court later.
OL,16,FTwo other men currently before the
OL,17,Fcourts will be further charged in
OL,18,Fconnection with the investigation.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
